<lb n="3"/>yathā-pradhāna-brāhmaṇa-purassarān sarvvān eva <unclear cert="low">kuṭumbinaḥ</unclear>
<lb n="4"/>kuśalam pr̥ṣṭvā mānayati pūrvva-rājabhir yu<unclear cert="low">ṣmākaṁ kūthera-śulyā</unclear><lb break="no" n="5"/>dhikaraṇābhyāṁ na praveṣṭavyam ity anugrahaḥ <unclear cert="low">kr̥tādhunā ma</unclear><lb break="no" n="6"/>yā sarvya-daṇḍa-nāyaka-mahā-pratihāra-śrī-bhaumagupta-vijñā<lb break="no" n="7"/>pitena liṅgval-māpcokādhikaraṇābhyām pa<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->ñcāparādha-dvāreṇa ca</supplied><lb break="no" n="8"/>turbhir apy adhikaraṇair nna praveṣṭavyam iti sthiti-paṭṭakeṇa prasādaḥ
<lb n="9"/>kr̥tas tad yūyam evaṁ viditvā yathaiva pūrvvam ājñā-śravaṇa-vidheyā<lb break="no" n="10"/>s tathaivāvalagana-parā bhūtvā nirvvr̥ta-viśvastāḥ sukhaṁ prativatsya<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->tha</supplied>
<lb n="11"/>ye cāsmad-<choice>
            <sic>b</sic>
            <corr>v</corr>
          </choice>aṁśyā rājāno bhavitāras tair api dharmma-gurūbhir gu<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->rū</supplied>-
